{"tid":1851719,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"車公的微言大義 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-01-30T06:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T16:14:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"151b7851a255d9a0b48a25fb539ef198b671c0e1","tid":1851719,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:44:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200130/20852467/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200130%2F20852467%2F&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rMg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=e20a15eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200130%2F20852467%2F&h=dfeef50e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200130/20852467/</a><br />\n<br />\n車公的微言大義 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200130/large/1580284553_f227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200130%2Flarge%2F1580284553_f227.jpg&h=6bc0d6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果日報》截圖<br />\n<br />\n恕我直言，許多「玄學界」代言人不是解籤，只是繞個圈子把民意套在籤文上，但求博得大眾好感。被騎劫的神明可能忿忿不平：&quot;Am I a joke to you？&quot; 須知解籤第一守則是「不忘初心」，即不要忽略你原先的問題。現在劉二世是問香港前程，不是替一條唔死都冇用嘅八婆求籤，對不對？因此，即使「馬謖帶兵」也隱含了對特首的嘲諷，但我們決不該把籤文寓意局限於政府，而須推而廣之，以及於香港整體社會。以下是我對車公那四句話的看法。<br />\n<br />\n「人生何在逞英豪」以典故論，是指馬謖擔任先鋒，不聽諸葛亮指揮，鋌而走險，致街亭失守，自己也被處斬。正如我昨天所說，馬謖本是諸葛亮的幕僚，擅於出謀劃策，track record甚佳。然而他一下子被提拔為統帥，則實戰經驗不足，難免大敗。套用現代管理學概念，車公是闡述「彼得原理」<span style=\"color: orange;\">（Peter Principle）：在一個機構內，人會因為某種優點，被擢升至他不勝任的職位。勿逞英豪，即勸大家量力而為&mdash;&mdash;回看當下時局，不就是對香港醫護的忠告嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「天理人情只要公」很簡單，強調的是「公道」。</span>耐人尋味的是，上句勸你勿逞英雄，這句卻大談公道，有什麼邏輯呢？兩句話的關聯，要在馬謖故事的語境才能理解。戰敗不一定問斬，但馬謖抗命，就只有死。當時蔣琬慨嘆馬是「智計之士」，問諸葛亮不可惜嗎，亮流着淚說：「孫武所以能制勝於天下者，用法明也。」即是說，諸葛亮是為了彰顯「公道」而殺馬謖的，馬謖不死，就不能服眾。<br />\n<br />\n「天眼恢恢疏不漏，定然作福福來從」，表面是車公的勉勵，即善有善報之意，實際是解釋「馬謖帶兵」為什麼是中籤。車公想說的是：本年是吉是凶，由你們自行決定，<span style=\"color: orange;\">只是要謹記兩點：一是做自己擅長的事，若你擅長策劃，今年就繼續策劃，千萬不要挑戰自己去帶兵；二是某件事做或不做、如何做，該以「公道」為依歸，想想眾人是否心服。</span>事事符合以上兩點，今年自然化險為夷，否則就難說了。<br />\n<br />\n最後提提大家：馬謖是湖北人，你懂的。 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"c89d7e5f3cda0d38164bfc61555a120bf3e435a0","tid":1851719,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d20a9d2a00143045e4f06a2cedb5d8fa464dc14","tid":1851719,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" cla